Definition: in a wasteful manner
Example: the United States, up to the 1920s, used fuel lavishly, mainly because it was so cheap
Synonyms: adj, all, wasteful, extravagant, lavishly, generous, lavish, in, a, manner, the, United, States, up, to, s, used, fuel, mainly, because, it, was, so, cheap
Category: adv.all
